    "created_at": "2016-03-31T12:18:38Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-03-31T12:18:38Z",
    "body": "As the documentation says, the enableLargerThanScreen option should \"Enable the window to be resized larger than screen\". It doesn't work for me (I was trying to create window larger than my screen resolution with more than 1920px in width and more than 1080px in height) and the result was only a 1920x1040px window. \n"
