    "created_at": "2016-04-01T02:12:29Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-04-01T02:12:29Z",
    "body": "I understand the problem now, on Windows there is a platform limitation that you can not create a window larger than the display, but you can resize the window to any size you want. So passing the window size to `BrowserWindow` won't work, but you can call `setSize` instead:\n\n``` js\ncapture.setSize(1920, 1080);\n```\n"
